**Root cause:** Classic off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts`, line 7.

```typescript
// BUGGY — stops one iteration early, skipping the last element
for (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {

// FIXED — iterates through all indices 0..length-1
