```

**Impact:** The `- 1` means when `i` reaches the last valid index (`length - 1`), the condition `i < length - 1` is already `false`, so the loop exits without processing that element. This also means a single-element array returns an empty array entirely.

**Only one file changes:** `src/utils.ts`, line 7 — remove `- 1` from the loop condition.

